---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';

import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro';

import bannerTop from '~/assets/images/1000dev/1000dev-detail.png';
import bannerBottom from '~/assets/images/1000dev/1000dev-detail-2.png';
import fundamental from '~/assets/images/1000dev/1000dev-fundamental.svg';
import gdgBali from '~/assets/images/1000dev/1000dev-gdgbali.png';
import devLogo from '~/assets/images/1000dev/1000dev-logo.svg';
import primakara from '~/assets/images/1000dev/1000dev-primakara.png';
import unbi from '~/assets/images/1000dev/1000dev-unbi.png';
import uxdIsland from '~/assets/images/1000dev/1000dev-uxd-island.png';
import webfeeling from '~/assets/images/1000dev/1000dev-webfeeling.png';
---

<Layout title="#1000Dev | SaranaTech" hideCta={true}>
  <main class="flex w-full flex-col items-center bg-white">
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <section
      class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[1170px] px-4 py-10 md:py-[60px] xl:px-0"
    >
      <h1
        class="max-w-[990px] text-[32px] leading-[48px] font-bold tracking-[1px] text-[#101010] capitalize md:text-[40px] md:leading-[60px]"
      >
        #1000Dev: Empowering Bali's Young Talented Developers Through Impactful
        Campaign
      </h1>
    </section>

    <!-- Hero Banner -->
    <section
      class="mx-auto mb-10 w-full max-w-[1170px] px-4 md:mb-[100px] xl:px-0"
    >
      <div
        class="relative h-[280px] w-full overflow-hidden bg-[#343434] md:h-[380px]"
      >
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
          <Image
            src={bannerTop}
            alt="1000Dev Banner"
            class="absolute h-full w-full object-cover object-center"
          />
        </div>

        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 z-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 md:flex-row md:p-0"
        >
          <div
            class="flex items-center md:absolute md:top-[146px] md:left-[80px]"
          >
            <Image
              src={devLogo}
              alt="Bali Movement #1000Devs"
              class="w-[200px] object-contain md:w-[294px]"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <section
      class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-[1170px] flex-col gap-[40px] px-4 pb-10 md:gap-[50px] md:pb-[100px] xl:px-0"
    >
      <!-- About -->
      <div class="flex w-full flex-col items-start gap-[20px]">
        <h2
          class="text-[20px] leading-[28.6px] font-bold tracking-[1px] text-[#101010] capitalize"
        >
          About #1000Dev
        </h2>
        <div
          class="flex w-full flex-col gap-4 text-[15px] leading-[28px] font-normal text-[#989898] md:max-w-[640px]"
        >
          <p>
            SaranaTech, in collaboration with industry leaders, developer
            communities, and educational institutions, has spearheaded an
            impactful campaign called #1000Dev to empower young and talented
            developers in Bali. This initiative aims to provide a platform for
            learning, collaboration, and growth, positioning Bali as a hub for
            tech talent.
          </p>
          <p>
            The primary objective of #1000Dev is to identify and support 1000
            talented developers in Bali, fostering their growth and creating
            pathways for success. By investing in the local tech community,
            SaranaTech aims to cultivate a pool of skilled professionals who can
            contribute to the development of Bali's digital economy.
          </p>
          <p>
            Through #1000Dev, SaranaTech has taken a proactive role in
            empowering and supporting young talented developers in Bali. By
            providing access to training, mentorship, networking opportunities,
            and job placements, the campaign has helped shape the future of the
            local tech industry. As a result, Bali's tech community is poised
            for growth and poised to make a significant impact on the digital
            landscape.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Engaging -->
      <div class="flex w-full flex-col items-start gap-[20px]">
        <h2
          class="text-[20px] leading-[28.6px] font-bold tracking-[1px] text-[#101010] capitalize"
        >
          Engaging The Developer Community
        </h2>
        <p
          class="w-full text-[15px] leading-[28px] font-normal text-[#989898] md:max-w-[640px]"
        >
          The #1000Dev campaign has garnered extensive support from the tech
          community in Bali, including the active involvement of the Google
          Developer Group Bali. This partnership has brought together
          experienced professionals and aspiring developers, fostering a vibrant
          ecosystem of knowledge sharing and mentorship.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Support -->
      <div class="flex w-full flex-col items-start gap-[20px]">
        <h2
          class="text-[20px] leading-[28.6px] font-bold tracking-[1px] text-[#101010] capitalize"
        >
          Support From Educational Institutions
        </h2>
        <p
          class="w-full text-[15px] leading-[28px] font-normal text-[#989898] md:max-w-[640px]"
        >
          Primakara University and Bali International University (UNBI) are
          among the educational institutions that have rallied behind the
          #1000Dev campaign. They have recognized the importance of nurturing
          and harnessing the potential of their students in the field of
          technology. By offering their resources and expertise, these
          institutions contribute to the campaign's success.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Objectives -->
      <div class="flex w-full flex-col items-start gap-[20px]">
        <h2
          class="text-[20px] leading-[28.6px] font-bold tracking-[1px] text-[#101010] capitalize"
        >
          #1000Dev Key Objectives:
        </h2>
        <ol
          class="w-full list-decimal space-y-4 pl-5 text-[15px] leading-[28px] font-normal text-[#989898] md:max-w-[640px]"
        >
          <li>
            <span class="font-semibold text-[#101010]"
              >Workshops and Training Sessions</span
            >
            <br />
            SaranaTech organizes hands-on workshops and training sessions conducted
            by experienced industry professionals. These sessions cover various topics,
            including programming languages, software development methodologies, and
            emerging technologies.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="font-semibold text-[#101010]">Bootcamp Program</span>
            <br />
            #1000Dev provides participants with access to a network of mentors who
            offer guidance, support, and industry insights. Mentors play a crucial
            role in nurturing talent and providing personalized advice to help young
            developers overcome challenges and reach their full potential.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="font-semibold text-[#101010]">Networking Events</span>
            <br />
            SaranaTech organizes networking events that bring together industry professionals,
            entrepreneurs, and developers. These events offer opportunities for knowledge-sharing,
            collaborations, and potential career advancements.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="font-semibold text-[#101010]"
              >Provision of work tools</span
            >
            <br />
            We provide work tools in the form of laptops / PCs for young talents with
            good coding talent but limited funds to get qualified work tools.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="font-semibold text-[#101010]"
              >Job Placement and Internship Opportunities</span
            >
            <br />
            Through partnerships with local businesses and organizations, #1000Dev
            facilitates job placements and internship opportunities for talented developers,
            enabling them to gain real-world experience and kickstart their careers.
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <!-- Secondary Banner -->
      <div
        class="relative mt-6 h-[380px] w-full overflow-hidden bg-[#343434] md:mt-10"
      >
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
          <Image
            src={bannerBottom}
            alt="1000Dev Secondary Banner"
            class="absolute h-full w-full object-cover object-center"
          />
        </div>

        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 z-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8 p-6 text-center"
        >
          <h3
            class="text-[24px] leading-[36px] font-semibold tracking-[1px] text-white capitalize md:text-[32px] md:leading-[44px]"
          >
            Helping Bali's best talented young people<br
              class="hidden md:block"
            />
            to become World-class developers
          </h3>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <Image
              src={devLogo}
              alt="Bali Movement #1000Devs"
              class="w-[120px] object-contain md:w-[147px]"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Partners Section -->
    <section
      class="flex w-full flex-col items-center border-t border-[#E5E5E5] bg-white px-4 py-10 md:py-[100px] xl:px-0"
    >
      <div
        class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-[1140px] flex-col items-center gap-10 md:gap-[70px]"
      >
        <h2
          class="text-center text-[24px] leading-[28.6px] font-bold tracking-[1px] text-[#101010] uppercase md:text-[26px]"
        >
          OUR PARTNERS
        </h2>

        <!-- Grid of logos -->
        <div class="grid w-full grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3">
          <!-- Partner 1 -->
          <div
            class="flex h-[160px] items-center justify-center border-r border-b border-[#e5e5e5] p-6 md:h-[221px]"
          >
            <Image
              src={gdgBali}
              alt="GDG Bali"
              class="w-[100px] object-contain mix-blend-multiply md:w-[150px]"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Partner 2 -->
          <div
            class="flex h-[160px] flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 border-b border-[#e5e5e5] p-6 md:h-[221px] md:border-r"
          >
            <Image
              src={webfeeling}
              alt="Webfeeling"
              class="w-[100px] object-contain mix-blend-multiply md:w-[150px]"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Partner 3 -->
          <div
            class="flex h-[160px] items-center justify-center border-r border-b border-[#e5e5e5] p-6 md:h-[221px] md:border-r-0"
          >
            <Image
              src={uxdIsland}
              alt="UXD Island"
              class="w-[100px] object-contain mix-blend-multiply md:w-[150px]"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Partner 4 -->
          <div
            class="flex h-[160px] items-center justify-center border-b border-[#e5e5e5] p-6 md:h-[221px] md:border-r md:border-b-0"
          >
            <Image
              src={fundamental}
              alt="Fundamental"
              class="w-[100px] object-contain mix-blend-multiply md:w-[150px]"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Partner 5 -->
          <div
            class="flex h-[160px] items-center justify-center border-r border-[#e5e5e5] p-6 md:h-[221px] md:border-r"
          >
            <Image
              src={unbi}
              alt="UNBI"
              class="w-[100px] object-contain mix-blend-multiply md:w-[150px]"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Partner 6 -->
          <div
            class="flex h-[160px] items-center justify-center p-6 md:h-[221px]"
          >
            <Image
              src={primakara}
              alt="Primakara"
              class="w-[100px] object-contain mix-blend-multiply md:w-[150px]"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
